data.description: Enjoy the benefits of living in the country and living only a few minutes away from the city. This ranch style home has had many updates made and gives you all the creature comforts you would expect. There is a large deck with electricity, lights and a cooking area. Also covered seating area right outside the master bedroom. Also there is a sunroom. There is a new area that is attached to the main house by a covered walkway that has two bedrooms, open kitchen, laundry, and a handicap accessible bath. the farm has 10 acres +or -. the land is pasture and wooded areas. It is fenced and cross fence.  A duck pond, 32x36 barn. Plus a 20x20 shop area with electric and vented with 1200 sq. ft. of storage. A 14x32 climatic controlled shed/shop with AC and lights. A 1 x32 lean to. Remember quiet country road that is easily accessible to town.  The appliances are all top of the line and convey with an acceptable offer.
